Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.52,0:00:04.35,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.73,0:00:11.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My life, led lacking all splendor, is heading toward a climax.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:13.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.74,0:00:16.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, come out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.24,0:00:20.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hanuki-san is a woman with no faults on an emotional or visual level,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:22.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but tonight she was just too...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.04,0:00:25.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Carry me away, before that person comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.42,0:00:27.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaori-san is a silent, lovely maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:30.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, we are fated to be apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.42,0:00:34.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we are not able to meet, then I cannot continue this relationship any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:38.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keiko-san is classy and ladylike, but I can't see her like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.31,0:00:46.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I choose Kaori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.65,0:00:47.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?!
