Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:22.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I was a brand-spanking new freshman university student
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:27.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and before me were held out circles' fliers far surpassing my own information intake potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:31.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And through each of them I could see \Na gateway to that rose-colored campus life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:38.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\be1\3c&H8D2120&\be1\fscx40\fscy40\c&H47FFF8&\t(0,140,\blur4)\t(140,240,\blur0)\t(0,270,\fscx120\fscy120\be3)\move(1002.087683,456.69145,962.004175,496.840149,0,280)\fnCalligrapher}Hero Show Association
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:40.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,A four year moratorium.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:43.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it would be good to grant children's aggressive dreams once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:47.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And perhaps a raven-haired maiden that \Nunderstands young boys' dreams may appear!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:56.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've turned over a new leaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:57.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.57,0:02:59.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:05.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:10.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There you are, Mochiguman...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:12.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Never defeating anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:14.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Never hurting anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:19.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before you know it, trouble's quieted down...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:21.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he's strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:23.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And has a big heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:27.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,A great, big, sincere heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:29.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, save Mochiguman!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:32.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:35.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those bad guys are trying to kidnap the girl, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:38.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone, make them change their ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:42.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Change your ways! Change your ways! \NChange your ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:45.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Change your ways! Change your ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:48.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, they ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:50.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good job, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:53.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like Mochiguman intervened yet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:56.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's Mochiguman for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:04:00.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:04.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got knocked around pretty good there...\N And it's only 3,000 yen a performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:09.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I want to scout you. Big money guaranteed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:13.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Order what you'd like at the engineering cafeteria and wait tomorrow at noon."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:15.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds pretty fishy to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:32.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:42.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I spend my days in the Shimogamo Yuusuisou boarding house behind Eizan Demachiyanagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:44.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a three-story wooden building that \Nlooks like it could collapse at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:46.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so run-down that just looking at it is worrisome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:48.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it'll be an important cultural landmark soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:51.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it's not difficult for me to imagine that no one would mind if it just vanished one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:54.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dear viewers, be not surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:57.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have been exchanging letters with \Na girl after some strange happenings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:59.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The most crucial things about exchanging letters are that they be handwritten
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:00.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and that you never meet your partner in correspondence,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:02.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,even should the very cauldron of hell be unleashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:04.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Far too oft that the elegant, precious
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:05.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,relationship you had fostered vanishes in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:10.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her name is Higuchi Keiko-san, and I can tell \Nher intelligence and education from her letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:12.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She is surely my ideal woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:16.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:17.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:30.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You speak of this to no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:32.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to keep it top secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:35.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see, I want you to be a certain woman's bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:37.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-Bodyguard?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:39.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not a dangerous job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:42.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just need to protect her while I am gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:44.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's been some... trouble lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:48.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are a great number of people who would try to deceive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:52.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you, my friend, I can rely on without reservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:54.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're as safe a bet as they come, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:57.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hear you're a late bloomer that is exceedingly shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:06:01.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Therefore I have no need to worry about you doing anything... funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:03.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will you handle this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:15.35,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:17.35,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:21.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaori is a very elegant woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:23.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want you to be very courteous to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:28.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I do not wish the world at large to learn of our private matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:32.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you speak about this to others, then, for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:41.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name was Jougasaki, and he was \Nthe president of the movie circle Misogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:43.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He handed me Kaori's entertainment manual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:45.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Things like no direct contact, her favorite drinks,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:48.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,not to run out of sweets, show her movies to make sure she doesn't get bored...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:49.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,All the essential principles were written down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:53.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:54.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't go getting any weird thoughts, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:04.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't think of her as a doll at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:08.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her hair was carefully combed, \Nand her clothes were neat and elegant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:10.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her makeup, and fingernails, and skin were all lovely...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:13.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did that elegant expression come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:15.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:18.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,...would be nice if Mr. Jougasaki came home soon, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:32.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Jougasaki is really a very simple and good person, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:34.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:37.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not like I can't understand how Mr. Jougasaki feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:41.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although I do think I'd prefer a flesh and blood woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:03.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so the days where I would receive
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:06.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,payment for guarding while \NMr. Jougasaki was out continued.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:11.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Mr. Jougasaki came back, \NI would be quickly thrown out of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:12.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those days...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:17.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with you lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:19.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems like you've been moving up in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:20.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:26.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're Kaori-san's bodyguard, isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:29.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.28,0:08:33.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please do not underestimate my information-gathering network.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:36.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jougasaki-san may act that way, but he's really pure-hearted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:38.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:41.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is a very refined kind of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:44.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a far cry from some "Dutch wife."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:47.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a very high-quality product called a "love doll."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:51.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Meaning that it's designed to be \Nloved and held dear by its owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:54.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,A boor like you who thinks of it as nothing more
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.55,0:08:56.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,than a tool to satisfy one's sexual desire wouldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:58.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:08:59.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then stay silent for eternity!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:01.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll have to decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:04.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I can't chat, I'll be so lonely I'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:06.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds good to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:11.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, I won't die as long as I'm making some idle chatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:15.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have no empathy for a soulless being like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:20.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be a bit more honest with yourself, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:23.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Jougasaki seemed to be busy at the moment shooting a film.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:26.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a modern remake of Alexander the Great
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:28.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,which was supposed to be the culmination of his work or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:30.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Within his circle he was very popular and charismatic,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:34.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but his favorite was, of course, Kaori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:37.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:45.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Around this time Mr. Jougasaki would be out of his room continuously,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:48.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and feeling sorry for the girl, I took tender care of her...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:51.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although, of course, she was just a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:54.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am exchanging letters with a real flesh and blood woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:55.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She always answers me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.95,0:09:59.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how beautiful Kaori-san looks to the eye, she will never respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:03.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:03.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:08.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey... Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:17.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The exquisite workmanship,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:21.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the delicate and lovely \Nworld Jougasaki had set up,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:24.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,made me think of her as a real person occasionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:32.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,OZ News is going great, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:34.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to you, Hanuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:37.78,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hanuki-san is a dental hygienist and an older member of the English Conversation Circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:41.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It became a habit of ours to go to a café after each session.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.03,0:10:43.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it seemed like she only drank \Nalcohol with people she knew well,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:45.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I had not yet been asked out for drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:48.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was wavering between the perverted dentist, Kubouzuka,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:51.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,who continuously asked her out, \Nand a boyfriend that neglected her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:55.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I finally received a letter from my pen-pal Keiko-san saying she wanted to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:57.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose that's proof that my literary skills
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:10:59.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,at lighting a maiden's heart on fire were nothing to scoff at.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:01.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, I was not able to meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.89,0:11:07.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why? Because the me within the letters was ever so slightly embellished from the me in reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:09.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true that's what I envision my ideal self to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.77,0:11:13.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it will take a bit of time for the current me to catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:19.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:23.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man, your place stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:26.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But my place isn't safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:28.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on to Kaori here for a while, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:49.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaori, I'm sorry. I know this is a filthy place, but please endure it for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:57.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll pay you the same hourly rate as before, at 24 hours a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:12:00.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, I don't have the cash on hand, \Nso please allow me to do a direct bank deposit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:03.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was how Kaori-san and I began living together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:06.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And wait, wasn't Mr. Jougasaki thinking a bit too little of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:09.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be that as it may, I never even dreamed that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:12.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,such a sweet campus life would be visited upon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:13.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,In these two past years I'd spent living uneventfully,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:16.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had never experienced such a brilliant event.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:20.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This and that... And two of each, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.26,0:12:24.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I returned from class, \NKaori-san was waiting for me in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:26.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That alone made the days enjoyable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:31.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was as if an intellectual, raven-haired maiden
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:35.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,whose dreams were filled with novels had borrowed a corner of my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:38.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of these days she will no longer be here, will she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:49.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They say love comes in all forms,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:52.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it is dangerous to become lost in the maze of such an insular love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:56.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I became fearful that I could no longer find the exit, I pressed deeper along the path.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:02.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:11.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am pleased to eat ramen for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:16.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I always wished to eat it once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:18.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure whether it's to your taste, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:23.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's quite beautiful, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:27.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, she's Jougasaki's girlfriend, \Nso please keep it a secret that we came here to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:31.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.96,0:13:41.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:49.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you ate ramen! I can smell it on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:54.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't eat in your room! Eat outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:59.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But well, I'm not getting any younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:01.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've just been doing what I felt like up till now,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:04.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but when I finish this movie I'm filming, I'm thinking of settling down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:10.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll graduate, get a job, \Nand then live once again with Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:16.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've been a great help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:18.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll come to pick up Kaori soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:19.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:33.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally I received an ultimatum from Keiko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:37.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I don't meet with her this time, \Nall communication will likely cease.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:41.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I was still not the man able to see Keiko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:44.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wanna go for some drinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:45.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:46.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a report I need to write today...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:48.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:51.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right. Good luck on your report!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:58.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And finally I was asked out for drinks by Hanuki-san as proof that we were close,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:15:00.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,yet I ended up going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:07.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why? Because tonight was the night \NJougasaki was coming to pick up Kaori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:11.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unless I aim to become some \NRenaissance man of the sexual arts,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:13.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I must narrow it down to one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:17.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaori-san, please wait a little while!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:18.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a matter of life and death!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.89,0:15:21.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I cannot allow Hanuki-san to be ruined by some perverted dentist's intentions!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:28.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, at the hotel's lounge I was \Nmet with an unexpected turn of events.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:30.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,For there in front of me was Mr. Jougasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:33.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Disgusted that he would try and place his hands on Hanuki-san while he was still with Kaori-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:37.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew I had no choice but to win this drinking battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:40.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somehow, I was victorious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:43.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:48.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then I was met with yet another unexpected turn of events.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:51.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:55.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:56.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've got to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.68,0:16:00.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is our once in a lifetime chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:03.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it... Kaori's the only one for me....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:05.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaori!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:08.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaori!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:22.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My body shakes thinking this might be the last time I hear your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:32.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I am loved once more by Jougasaki, a different me will surely sprout.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:35.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The me who is here now only exists in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.35,0:16:37.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaori...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:39.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please take me with you and escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:41.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:51.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,"We're eloping. Thank you for everything. - Kaori," eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:53.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Jougasaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:05.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaori-san is getting wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:19.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Kaori-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:25.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay. I'm glad. I've never gotten wet from the rain before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:27.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaori-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:31.78,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You there, student...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:33.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The old woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.36,0:17:37.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Student, what might you wish to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:39.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't asked you anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:42.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. You are dissatisfied, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.79,0:17:45.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said I had no idea what you're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:50.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, opportunity is always dangling in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:52.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please grab on to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:55.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That'll be 7,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.13,0:17:57.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:05.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the rain lets up,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:08.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,we'll head to Kyoto station and buy \Ntrain tickets to as far away as we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.77,0:18:10.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we'll head to a country at the end of the earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:12.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and live in a small town in a small house...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:14.78,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Working in a strange land will surely be tough,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:16.78,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but seeing your smile when \NI come home will give me cheer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:18.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before long, we'll have a child,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:21.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and your parents who were against this will surely come to accept me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:24.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The days and months pass by and at length we have grandchildren.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:27.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I realize I have lived only for that day, \Ntears fall from my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:28.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They are the happiest days of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:32.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But suddenly you fall ill, \Nand I grasp your hand, nursing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:35.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Smiling, you say "I'm so glad I met you."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:37.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But no, that's what I should be saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:40.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't we promise that I'd be the first to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:42.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just so glad we were able to be together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.55,0:18:46.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If this isn't an opportunity, then what is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:49.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey now, this here's a 100% full-blow opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:52.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at her face, she's waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:54.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaori-san isn't like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:56.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how high-class her face looks,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:18:59.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,inside her heart is the same burning passion that's inside yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:00.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:02.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hell no it isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:03.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you think she came with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.62,0:19:05.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's always with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:07.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,See? She's been looking at you the whole time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:12.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before we part, I want to share your warmth...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:16.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you let me feel like I am loved?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:18.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaori-san, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:22.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know that to you this isn't passionate, burning love.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.55,0:19:24.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But right now the warmth of your hand
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:28.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,is the one thing that can make me feel like I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:32.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't? Is it because I'm not a real person?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:34.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I'm a doll without a heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:36.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, Kaori-san! That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:38.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I also...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:40.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.87,0:19:52.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're too beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:54.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't run away, you coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:57.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want to spend the rest of your life a pitiful late-bloomer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:19:59.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're okay with being called a "safe bet"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:01.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about her shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:03.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think she wants you to thrust \Nyour burning passion upon her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:05.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's been waiting this whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:07.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:09.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am, after all, a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:11.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then make her a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:14.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:17.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you come and do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:21.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it... I'll do it for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.24,0:20:22.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:26.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop! What are you doing?
